(1) Coney Island (Reigelmann) Boardwalk, north side, west from Stillwell Ave., to West 15th Street, showing from right to left the Stauch, Klarinet, Bushman and Oriole salt water baths.

July 8, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, a more limited view.

August 9, 1932.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) The same as No. 2, looking eastward.

August 8, 1932.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Islands - Coney Island - [Riegelmann boardwalk - Bushman Baths - Klarnet Baths - Oriole Baths - Stauch Baths.] - [Brooklyn: Stillwell Avenue - 15th Street (West).]
